{"tid":1793232,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"天水圍中彈聰仔蘇醒 反應遲緩","createTime":"2019-12-22T08:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T04:26:37.000Z","uid":25558,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"d865019ee54f16bceb54f99abbe4b81c8c80a7b6","tid":1793232,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T08:53:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191222/6QMLV3QC5FPEXFMHQXF53DMT74/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191222%2F6QMLV3QC5FPEXFMHQXF53DMT74%2F&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctD4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=c1cc0db5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191222%2F6QMLV3QC5FPEXFMHQXF53DMT74%2F&h=1bf013d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191222/6QMLV3QC5FPEXFMHQXF53DMT74/</a><br />\n<br />\n天水圍中彈聰仔蘇醒 反應遲緩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】父母離世、與兄長相依為命的15歲少年傅同學（聰仔），今年11月在天水圍疑被防暴警察發射催淚彈擊中頭部重創，經搶救後持續昏迷，在深切治療部（ICU）留醫一個月，近日終於蘇醒。一直協助聰仔的基督教信義會青少年服務總監竺永洪透露，聰仔現可進食及說話，惟對外界反應仍遲緩，康復時間難以估計。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：習上台後「電視認罪」大增<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191222/large/1576942690_7373.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191222%2Flarge%2F1576942690_7373.jpg&h=dad816c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聰仔當日疑被防暴警發射催淚彈擊中頭部，重傷倒地。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可進食及正常對話<br />\n<br />\n聰仔現已由ICU轉到普通病房留醫。竺永洪回應《蘋果》查詢時表示，聰仔暫未能下床，但可進食及正常對話，也認得兄長，情緒亦平復。他指由於聰仔昏迷了一段時間，料需較長時間康復，難以評估進度，至於聰仔何時才能出院及重返校園，目前仍言之尚早。聰仔兄長也透過竺永洪向社會轉達，感謝各界的慰問和支持。<br />\n<br />\n上月13日全港三罷期間，天水圍晚上爆發警民衝突，逾百人包圍天水圍警署，防暴警察向人群發射至少50枚催淚彈驅散。聰仔在天水圍新北江商場對開疑被催淚彈擊中頭部重創，顱骨骨折，送院後需即時進行開腦手術，經搶救後雖沒生命危險，但持續昏迷，只間中手和頭部有輕微反應，直至近日才完全蘇醒。<br />\n<br />\n聰仔父母先後因病離世，與兄長相依為命。他遇襲後，兄長辭工照料，各界也伸出援手，候任區議員林進亦幫忙籌得60多萬元，用作解決其醫療費及生活開支。<br />\n<br />\n■記者王家文"},{"pid":"b9659c304ec9d8b1581b022bea29258cc33294c6","tid":1793232,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T08:54:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">和你坐  Stuck稅局</span><br />\n12月23日 星期一<br />\n時間 : 12:00<br />\n地點 : 稅務大樓<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「星火不息 燃點國際」集會</span><br />\n日期︰2019年12月23日(一)<br />\n時間︰晚上七時至九時<br />\n地點︰中環愛丁堡廣場<br />\n主辦方︰張崑陽、候任中西區區議員梁晃維、民間集會團隊<br />\n*已通知警方，待發不反對通知書"},{"pid":"ddc105cd8ca8c5aad24ced4aa01af9fa727c859b","tid":1793232,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T08:55:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62082cc47fcd9bb9ea2ef364d853fbced855301d","tid":1793232,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T08:56:09.000Z","msg":"【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【行動po】【求推】點解1223去稅局 連登冇人講？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1792093\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1792093</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n點解1223稅局冇人提？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1781990\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1781990</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FbPAwwX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFbPAwwX.jpg&h=af432327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WvBryAY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWvBryAY.jpg&h=fea3e57a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7grryiG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7grryiG.jpg&h=5fde20aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ddDxvuv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FddDxvuv.jpg&h=525dd049&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<i