睇開的球迷入嚟一齊討論傾下波經。以老帶新，由資深球迷帶新手球迷入門，交換資訊，降低香港睇波門檻，等愈來愈多球迷入場撐港足，重建香港球巿。<br />\n<br />\n入group嘅可以講低自己中意邊隊，得閒約埋一齊去睇波。仲等咩快d入嚟<br />\n<br />\n光復香港由重建港足文化開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctD4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=07b7fcd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LCJafhSHT6-AthgR0r3GUQ</a>"},{"pid":"bc6b36ca773e45f3f565c6e434c3f55e12bf47a0","tid":1793232,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T08:58:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ca54853b09b92e2e8256d811bb2b6522b21dd741","tid":1793232,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T10:29:01.000Z","msg":"大家星期日有時間，記住加入香港金融業職工總會做會員呀！<br />\n<br />\n我哋可唔可以為大家發聲，可以做到咩地步，全靠會員的支持<br />\n<br />\n冇會員，政府點解要理你呢，資方點解要理你呢...<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好等，今日就加入啦<br />\n<br />\nPS: 就算唔係金融界的同業，都麻煩like and share，俾多一個人睇到，就多一分機會團結同路人，拜托拜托🙏<br />\n<br />\n#香港金融業職工總會<br />\n#香港金總<br />\n#HKFU<br />\n#收會員<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107457800635080/posts/159723118741881/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107457800635080%2Fposts%2F159723118741881%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=QEbR3JiquQCbCEiBABctD4uQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=73bc12ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107457800635080/posts/159723118741881/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"06f9c4f00b5dc3c8536e55182dbaf66b9d7a9c47","tid":1793232,"uid":4521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:28:40.000Z","msg":"林進D錢交左出黎未?"},{"pid":"c1e6c55eaed8ff45167cfa573fbd44cb576e4d67","tid":1793232,"uid":70771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T06:31:18.000Z","msg":"推啊，唔好咁快就唔記得左聰仔啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21265835b037778207480d2670307b174926a23","tid":1793232,"uid":89006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite